[2], 8 p.
s.n., [Edinburgh : 1661]
Attribution from Wing (2nd ed.). Place and date of publication suggested by Wing (2nd ed.). Manuscript notes on p. [1], faded and somewhat illegible. Imperfect: dark, print show-through, with some loss of text. Satire in the form of a news-letter, concerning a horse race. Cf. National Library of Scotland. Reproduction of original in: National Library of Scotland.
